-- ft.page: Deployment

-- ft.h1: `ssh` into the server

-- ft.code:
lang: sh
caption: ssh into the server

\$ ssh -i /path/to/secret.pem ec2-user@public-server-ip


-- ft.h1: Updating the `django` app codebase

-- ft.code:
lang: sh
caption: Update the codebase and restart server

\$ cd www/
$ git pull origin main
$ cd src/dj/
$ python3 manage.py migrate # Optional step
$ sudo systemctl restart django-app